00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:36.180 align:middle line:84%
I have this little bit
on one of my programs

00:19:36.180 --> 00:19:37.955 align:middle line:84%
called Whitewater
Rafting at 101.

00:19:37.955 --> 00:19:38.780 align:middle line:90%
>> [LAUGHS]

00:19:38.780 --> 00:19:41.430 align:middle line:84%
