a point many people miss.

00:20:32.100 --> 00:20:34.260 align:middle line:90%
Everybody is in sales.

00:20:34.260 --> 00:20:36.060 align:middle line:84%
Sales is such an
incredible skill,

00:20:36.060 --> 00:20:37.800 align:middle line:84%
