of selling cars

00:20:39.960 --> 00:20:41.890 align:middle line:84%
or compute systems
or anything else.

00:20:41.890 --> 00:20:44.200 align:middle line:84%
You need to sell
yourself to get a job.

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:46.510 align:middle line:84%
You need to sell
yourself to get a spouse.

00:20:46.510 --> 00:20:48.880 align:middle line:84%
You need to sell
yourself to get a raise.

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:51.100 align:middle line:84%
And so even people
who say, gee, I

00:20:51.100 --> 00:20:53.200 align:middle line:84%
don't want anything
to do with sales--

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:56.923 align:middle line:84%
you have to understand it's
just that anything is sales.

00:20:56.923 --> 00:20:58.090 align:middle line:90%
>> You are selling yourself.

00:20:58.090 --> 00:20:59.800 align:middle line:10%
>> And so, selling
with confidence--

00:20:59.800 --> 00:21:04.150 align:middle line:10%
and why do most people not like
