00:21:04.150 --> 00:21:05.020 align:middle line:10%
not good at selling?

00:21:05.020 --> 00:21:06.770 align:middle line:90%
There it is-- confidence.

00:21:06.770 --> 00:21:08.590 align:middle line:84%
And so while that
program is designed

00:21:08.590 --> 00:21:10.630 align:middle line:84%
