00:21:16.940 --> 00:21:17.630 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:21:17.630 --> 00:21:18.470 align:middle line:90%
>> But it is true.

00:21:18.470 --> 00:21:20.470 align:middle line:84%
And I remember someone,
